.TH smi-localhost-location "1" "February 2026" "SMI Toolset" "SMI Localhost Location Command"
.SH NAME
smi-localhost-location \- print the SMI localhost configuration directory path
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-localhost-location
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The
.B smi-localhost-location
command prints the path to the SMI localhost-specific configuration directory.
.PP
.B NOTE:
This command is deprecated.
